This project analyzes a flight booking dataset from EaseMyTrip to extract meaningful insights and predict flight prices using Linear Regression.

Dataset
The dataset includes details such as:Airlines,Destination,Number of Stops,Ticket Prices
Methodology
Data Preprocessing – Cleaning and preparing data for analysis.
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) – Identifying patterns and trends.
Statistical Hypothesis Testing – Extracting meaningful insights.
Model Training – Using Linear Regression to predict flight prices.
Objective
To help passengers make informed booking decisions by predicting flight prices based on historical data.

Tools Used
Python
Pandas, NumPy
Matplotlib, Seaborn
Scikit-Learn
